

     
      Oh he's there alright.  Closer to the window, staring in at you.  What you hear in your mind is "History, repeats."  The restaurant is in chaos. Patrons and staff make for the door. Liz slams Tom down onto the table, wresting the gun from his hand with Hax helping.  Missy is up and going past you toward where Samantha is. Only Robin is sitting calmly and serenly at the table.  Somewhere in the fog of background noise, you hear "She's been shot!"  
     
    
